title: AWS Glacier: Vault
agents: aws
catalog: cloud/aws
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the archives of AWS/Glacier vaults and reports

 - the number of archives

 - size of the vault

 To make this check work you have to configure the related
 special agent {Amazon Web Services (AWS)}.

 There are no default levels set for the vault size.
 Upper levels are configurable.

item:
 Name of the vault.

inventory:
 One service is created for each vault.
